---
config:
  theme: dark
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as Client / SDK
    participant Frontend as Dynamo Frontend + KV Router<br/>(Gateway / API / Routing / KV Index State)
    participant EncodeSidecar as Encode Dynamo Sidecar
    participant EncodeEngine as Native Encode Engine Server<br/>(vLLM - vision/audio encoder)
    participant PrefillSidecar as Prefill Dynamo Sidecar
    participant PrefillEngine as Native Prefill Engine Server<br/>(vLLM)
    participant DecodeSidecar as Decode Dynamo Sidecar
    participant DecodeEngine as Native Decode Engine Server<br/>(vLLM)

    Client->>Frontend: Send request<br/>(prompt + media URLs, params, stream=true)

    Frontend->>Frontend: Authenticate / authorize
    Frontend->>Frontend: Normalize to Dynamo request schema
    Frontend->>Frontend: Detect multimodal media<br/>(token_ids carry un-expanded placeholder markers)
    Frontend->>Frontend: Select encode worker using router

    Frontend->>EncodeSidecar: Forward Dynamo encode request<br/>(media URLs / data URIs)

    EncodeSidecar->>EncodeSidecar: Normalize to OpenEngine encode request schema<br/>(media items, ENGINE_ROLE_ENCODE)
    EncodeSidecar->>EncodeEngine: Invoke encode over OpenEngine API

    EncodeEngine->>EncodeEngine: Normalize to vLLM encode request schema
    EncodeEngine->>EncodeEngine: Fetch / decode media + run vision/audio encoder<br/>(produce mm embeddings, populate encoder cache)

    EncodeEngine-->>EncodeSidecar: Return EncodeReady over OpenEngine API<br/>(EmbeddingSessionRef - embeddings stay on engine GPU/NIXL)
    EncodeSidecar->>EncodeSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo encode response schema

    EncodeSidecar-->>Frontend: Return Dynamo encode response<br/>(embedding session handle)

    Frontend->>Frontend: Update routing state from encode result
    Frontend->>Frontend: Select prefill worker using KV router

    Frontend->>PrefillSidecar: Forward Dynamo prefill request<br/>(token_ids + placeholder markers, embedding session ref)

    PrefillSidecar->>PrefillSidecar: Normalize to OpenEngine prefill request schema<br/>(carries embedding_session)
    PrefillSidecar->>PrefillEngine: Invoke prefill over OpenEngine API

    PrefillEngine->>PrefillEngine: Normalize to vLLM prefill request schema
    PrefillEngine->>PrefillEngine: Attach embedding session

    EncodeEngine-->>PrefillEngine: Transfer mm embeddings<br/>(NIXL / RDMA - engine-to-engine, opaque handle only via sidecar)
    PrefillEngine->>PrefillEngine: Execute prefill<br/>(expand placeholders with embeddings + KV cache population)

    PrefillEngine-->>PrefillSidecar: Return PrefillReady over OpenEngine API<br/>(KvSessionRef, usage, errors)
    PrefillSidecar->>PrefillSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo prefill response schema

    PrefillSidecar-->>Frontend: Return Dynamo prefill response<br/>(KV transfer params)

    Frontend->>Frontend: Update KV router state from prefill result
    Frontend->>Frontend: Select decode worker using KV router

    Frontend->>DecodeSidecar: Forward Dynamo decode request<br/>(KV transfer params, params)

    DecodeSidecar->>DecodeSidecar: Normalize to OpenEngine decode request schema
    DecodeSidecar->>DecodeEngine: Invoke decode over OpenEngine API

    DecodeEngine->>DecodeEngine: Normalize to vLLM decode request schema
    DecodeEngine->>DecodeEngine: Attach KV transfer params

    PrefillEngine-->>DecodeEngine: Transfer KV cache<br/>(NIXL - engine-to-engine)
    DecodeEngine->>DecodeEngine: Execute decode<br/>(generate tokens from transferred KV)

    DecodeEngine-->>DecodeSidecar: Stream response over OpenEngine API<br/>(tokens, usage, finish reason, errors)
    DecodeSidecar->>DecodeSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo response schema

    DecodeSidecar-->>Frontend: Stream Dynamo response
    Frontend-->>Client: Stream response

    par Event plane
        EncodeEngine-->>EncodeSidecar: Emit OpenEngine events<br/>(request status / encoder-cache / embedding session / metrics)
        EncodeSidecar->>EncodeSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo routing state
        EncodeSidecar-->>Frontend: Publish Dynamo routing + state events<br/>(capacity / embedding metadata / request status)

        PrefillEngine-->>PrefillSidecar: Emit OpenEngine events<br/>(request status / KV events / metrics)
        PrefillSidecar->>PrefillSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo routing state
        PrefillSidecar-->>Frontend: Publish Dynamo routing + state events<br/>(capacity / KV metadata / request status)

        DecodeEngine-->>DecodeSidecar: Emit OpenEngine events<br/>(request status / KV events / metrics)
        DecodeSidecar->>DecodeSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo routing state
        DecodeSidecar-->>Frontend: Publish Dynamo routing + state events<br/>(capacity / KV metadata / request status)
    and State update
        Frontend->>Frontend: Update KV router state<br/>(embedding session, KV index, worker capacity, request status)
    end
